  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desolated District is a survival crafting game set in a post-apocalyptic dystopia. Scavenge, craft, build, and battle to survive in a sprawling, decaying urban environment now overrun with looming threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/0cf9f1e9e5fc1f20b2b16ead6b9e4f81.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Vast Post-Apocalyptic World </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and Customize Your Base </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow and Harvest Your Own Crops </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft, Upgrade, and Survive </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in Challenging Combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression and Skill Development </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource Management and Strategy </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/18ec22f058b6d8145bfe075746e8d728.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/18ec22f058b6d8145bfe075746e8d728.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/58c6cea0af3ae29f942e3309834e9e4a.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse an expansive district filled with abandoned homes, crumbling factories, and hidden underground areas. Uncover secrets, scavenge for resources, and encounter dangers lurking in every corner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/7290b951dd7c31468b9b09b3c7485e45.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/7290b951dd7c31468b9b09b3c7485e45.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/a8089cb6455eab58a16893240700a654.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct your ultimate shelter from scratch! Design, expand, and decorate your base with a wide variety of furniture, structures, and functional stations. Create a home that not only looks great but keeps you safe from the harsh environment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/6b7eb03f235d82088b3cc0539067344c.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/6b7eb03f235d82088b3cc0539067344c.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/c69ccd7ed22aba93e8785ef3dca0e2e4.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials from your environment to craft essential gear, tools, and items. Upgrade your workstations and unlock advanced crafting recipes as you progress. Everything you need to survive can be crafted if you’re resourceful enough. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/713cf127811f77a7878d2a43c71eb08d.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/713cf127811f77a7878d2a43c71eb08d.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desolated District is a survival crafting game set in a post-apocalyptic dystopia. Scavenge, craft, build, and battle to survive in a sprawling, decaying urban environment now overrun with looming threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/0cf9f1e9e5fc1f20b2b16ead6b9e4f81.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Vast Post-Apocalyptic World </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and Customize Your Base </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow and Harvest Your Own Crops </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft, Upgrade, and Survive </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in Challenging Combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression and Skill Development </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource Management and Strategy </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/18ec22f058b6d8145bfe075746e8d728.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/18ec22f058b6d8145bfe075746e8d728.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/58c6cea0af3ae29f942e3309834e9e4a.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse an expansive district filled with abandoned homes, crumbling factories, and hidden underground areas. Uncover secrets, scavenge for resources, and encounter dangers lurking in every corner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/7290b951dd7c31468b9b09b3c7485e45.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/7290b951dd7c31468b9b09b3c7485e45.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/a8089cb6455eab58a16893240700a654.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct your ultimate shelter from scratch! Design, expand, and decorate your base with a wide variety of furniture, structures, and functional stations. Create a home that not only looks great but keeps you safe from the harsh environment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/6b7eb03f235d82088b3cc0539067344c.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/6b7eb03f235d82088b3cc0539067344c.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/c69ccd7ed22aba93e8785ef3dca0e2e4.webp?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials from your environment to craft essential gear, tools, and items. Upgrade your workstations and unlock advanced crafting recipes as you progress. Everything you need to survive can be crafted if you’re resourceful enough. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/713cf127811f77a7878d2a43c71eb08d.poster.avif?t=1749156409\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454070/extras/713cf127811f77a7878d2a43c71eb08d.webm?t=1749156409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
